These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, reggae, metal
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | gospel | d&b | metal |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, lizard, horse, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | fish | horse | lizard | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, writing, sudoku, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | sudoku | woodworking | writing | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, ship, boat
1. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | ship | quad-bike | subway | boat |

